long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The best math study extension that works.

MathChimp uses OCR and complex algorithms to scan and solve your math problems no matter how hard they are. We can solve complex word problems, decipher tricky integrals, and find the solution to just about any problem you have for us.

You don't have to spend hours trying to figure out your math homework anymore. MathChimp is also fully undetectable, and works like a charm. If you are enrolled in any math course, MathChimp is the perfect tool to enhance and speed up your learning progress! Visit us at mathchimp.ai
